Date: Fri, 13 Feb 2026 11:26:37 -0300
Subject: [PATCH] MGS-6823: Manually apply Wayland sync logic

This patch adds support for VK_COMPOSITE_ALPHA_OPAQUE and includes
necessary Wayland event polling logic for i.MX platforms.

Upstream-Status: Inappropriate [i.MX specific]
Signed-off-by: Vagner Nörnberg  <vagner.nornberg@ossystems.com.br>

